---
name: Comic Book
description: Style preset — Comic Book
tags: [style, creative, aspect-3:4]
---
Render in a bold comic book illustration style with thick black ink outlines, Ben-Day dot shading patterns, and a vivid primary color palette of red, blue, yellow, and green. Text should appear in comic-style lettering with key labels in speech bubbles or caption boxes. Add dynamic action lines and POW/ZAP-style emphasis marks around important connections. The result should look like a page ripped from a tech-themed graphic novel -- bold, punchy, and impossible to scroll past.
